QuestData.Title: The Sands of Silithus
QuestData.Description: Let's see... oh, here's a good one! Silithus!$b$bSo, apparently the Cenarion Circle needs assistance with an insect infestation of some sort.$b$b<Vizzie shivers.>$b$bUgh! No thanks, not for me. I'm perfectly happy freezing to death here in Everlook if the alternative is bugs.$b$bHmm... it says here that visitors should speak with Windcaller Proudhorn, and the easiest way to get there is via the path up Un'Goro Crater's northwestern cliffs.$b$bYou interested?
QuestData.LogDescription: Report to Windcaller Proudhorn at Cenarion Hold in Silithus.
QuestData.RewardText: Welcome to Cenarion Hold.$b$b<Windcaller Proudhorn brushes some snow off of your shoulder.>$b$bYou've certainly come from far off.
